{"tid":1036163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《還願》遭支那封殺，全球銷售量反突破100萬套?","createTime":"2019-02-25T04:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T09:55:24.000Z","uid":185780,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e661063acecbfb7b993ff09512a67d253c1f89ca","tid":1036163,"uid":185780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:46:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>早前情況:</strong><br />\n<br />\n國產恐怖解謎遊戲《還願》，傳出遊戲場景裡的黃色符咒上寫著「呢嘛叭唭」，以及蓋有「習近平小熊維尼」篆體字紅印，被眼尖網友認為是暗批大陸領導人習近平，引發大陸網友氣憤抵制，中國代理商隨即終止合作關係，不過《還願》在Steam平台銷售上似乎不受影響，仍待排行榜第一，銷售量比23日多10萬套，目前全球已售出超過 20 萬套。<br />\n<br />\n根據 Steam 數據調查網站 Steamspy 顯示，《還願》19日上線當天發售 7 萬 5000 多套，23日超過 10 萬大關，經過符咒風波，反而銷售數字大攀升，全球已超越 20 萬套，銷售量逆勢成長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/mit-%E9%82%84%E9%A1%98-%E9%81%AD%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%8D%E9%A3%86%E5%94%AE10%E8%90%AC%E5%A5%97-092000137.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2Fmit-%25E9%2582%2584%25E9%25A1%2598-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%25B0%2581%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E9%258A%25B7%25E5%2594%25AE%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%25A3%2586%25E5%2594%25AE10%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25A5%2597-092000137.html&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8f7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=11428b8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/mit-%E9%82%84%E9%A1%98-%E9%81%AD%E5%B0%81%E6%AE%BA-%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E9%8A%B7%E5%94%AE%E9%87%8F%E5%8F%8D%E9%A3%86%E5%94%AE10%E8%90%AC%E5%A5%97-092000137.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>最新銷售量:</strong><br />\n<br />\n還願目前擁有份數達到25萬份(更新破百萬數字):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1551067744.A.396.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FC_Chat%2FM.1551067744.A.396.html&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8f7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=d05766ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/C_Chat/M.1551067744.A.396.html</a><br />\n<br />\nSteamspy:<br />\n<a href=\"https://steamspy.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamspy.com%2F&d=g2%2Fo6b0QjPi1xWtu1PcU8f7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=136e8257\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamspy.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nOwners: 1,000,000 .. 2,000,000<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UDYeL3w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUDYeL3w.png&h=43413b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cA8QvC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cA8QvC.jpg&h=7a22a0c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0da711d37cec94327d0cd7896054687783b6589a","tid":1036163,"uid":169994,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"隻game個開發商識玩，愈封殺，啲蝗虫就愈搶住玩"},{"pid":"aa9b48ddca9589d5b63dbec6cf60b82bc3febaa9","tid":1036163,"uid":54733,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:48:46.000Z","msg":"中國封殺還願搞到全球報導<br />\n<br />\n多謝中國幫手賣免費廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31feaba4667c60c384256daa5e6627567a5d543","tid":1036163,"uid":190168,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"0da711d37cec94327d0cd7896054687783b6589a","tid":1036163,"uid":169994,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"隻game個開發商識玩，愈封殺，啲蝗虫就愈搶住玩"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"邊忽識玩？ 爆出黎嗰時即刻掠水改走舊野喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b71fb7471f073b9e79d16eb5514aba125e9086","tid":1036163,"uid":103156,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwTROt9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwTROt9.png&h=0bdfe0de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8b0628df3ee01bd37b25cf03e9a835f7393ee93","tid":1036163,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a31feaba4667c60c38425